title: Passing the Torch (Time Life - Vietnam Experience).pdf
description:
Passing the Torch (The Vietnam Experience)
Boston Publishing Company | 1981 | ISBN: 0939526018 | English | 220 pages | PDF | 40.3 MB

This particular volume of "The Vietnam Experience" series takes the reader through events concerning Vietnam beginning with the Second World War and ending with the presidency of Diem. There are many seldom seen photos in the book which the reader will find appealing. Discusses the development of Vietnam's fight for independence from France and analyzes the origins of the United States involvement in the Vietnam War
